msgstr "Verwendung dynamischer Platzhalter in einer E-Mail-Vorlage."

#: ../../content/applications/general/companies/email_template.rst:151
msgid ""
"Each unique combination of :guilabel:`Fields`, :guilabel:`Sub-models` and "
