"`Mailjet: How can I configure my SMTP parameters? "
"<https://documentation.mailjet.com/hc/articles/360043229473>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Mailjet: Wie kann ich meine SMTP-Parameter konfigurieren? "
"<https://documentation.mailjet.com/hc/articles/360043229473>`_"

