"that has a built-in firewall, can prevent the :abbr:`HTTPS (Hypertext "
"Transfer Protocol Secure)` certificate from generating."
msgstr ""
"Darüber hinaus kann eine Firewall auch verhindern, dass das :abbr:`HTTPS "
